    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been garage-kept and pampered like a member of the family\u2014honestly, it still smells new inside! It\u2019s in truly incredible shape, and while I hate to see it go, I know the next owner is going to fall in love just like I did. There\u2019s a tiny, almost invisible scuff on the rear wheel from a high curb, but other than that, she\u2019s practically flawless. Come by, have a coffee, and see her for yourself!",
